@page "/faq"
<PageTitle>FAQ</PageTitle>

<div class="faq-container">

    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>How do I adopt a dog?</h2>
        <p>
            Complete an adoption application online.<br />
            Once your identity has been confirmed and we've ensured that you fulfill all of the requirements necessary to adopt, then your application will be sent through.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>What is included in the adoption fee?</h2>
        <p>
            The adoption fee covers:<br />
            - Vaccinations<br />
            - Spaying/neutering<br />
            - Microchipping<br />
            - Basic medical care
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>Do you allow out-of-state adoptions?</h2>
        <p>
            We prioritize local adoptions but may allow out-of-state adoptions if transportation and a home check can be arranged.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>Can I adopt a dog if I live in an apartment?</h2>
        <p>
            Yes, as long as your landlord permits pets and you can provide a safe and suitable environment for the dog.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>Are all dogs spayed or neutered?</h2>
        <p>
            Yes, all dogs are spayed or neutered before adoption unless they are too young or have a medical condition preventing the procedure.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>What if the dog has special needs?</h2>
        <p>
            We provide full information about the dog's medical or behavioral needs before adoption. Our team will work with you to ensure you're prepared to care for a special needs dog.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>What should I bring when adopting?</h2>
        <p>
            Please bring:<br />
            - A valid photo ID<br />
            - Proof of residence (e.g., utility bill or lease agreement)<br />
            - A leash and collar to take your dog home
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>How do I contact you?</h2>
        <p>
            You can reach us at:<br />
            <strong>Email:</strong> PawfectMatch@gmail.com<br />
            <strong>Phone:</strong> 777-777-7777<br />
            <strong>Address:</strong> 1844 10th ST N
        </p>
    </div>

</div>

